      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Your Operating System is Your Agent's Day-One Onboarding</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">When you hire an employee, you give them an onboarding packet. When you deploy an agent, what do you give it? If the answer is "a prompt and good luck," you are setting it up to fail.</p>
